ASoC: fsl-asoc-card: add support for TLV320AIC32x4 codec

The TLV320AIC32x4 is commonly used on TQ-Systems starterkit mainboards
for i.MX-based SoMs (i.MX6Q/DL, i.MX6UL, i.MX7) and LS1021A.

